  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "# Message status changes from sent to delivered when messaging with a blocked contact\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nWhen a contact sends a message to a blocked contact while the blocked contact is active, the status of the message changes from sent to delivered which should not happen. We want when messaging with a blocked contact the message status to remain as sent\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nMessage status remains sent when sending a message to a blocked contact\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nMessage status changed to delivered when sending a message to a blocked\r\ncontact when the contact is active or comes online\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status\r\n2) Block a contact from your contacts lists\r\n3) Confirm the blocked contact is active\r\n4) Send a message to the blocked contact\r\n4) Confirm that message status changes from sent to delivered\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
